abstract: Two indexes are now ahead for the year. Markets rose on improved new home sales and a higher earnings estimate from FedEx.
snippet: Two indexes are now ahead for the year. Markets rose on improved new home sales and a higher earnings estimate from FedEx.
lead_paragraph: Exchanges on Wall Street got a strong start to a week that will end on Friday with the release of a crucial indicator: the economy’s second-quarter growth.

headline.main: Stocks Finish Stronger; Dow and Nasdaq Reach Highest Points Since April
headline.print_headline: Stocks Finish Stronger; Dow and Nasdaq Reach High Points for the Year

byline.original: By Matthew Saltmarsh and Susanna G. Kim
